{"tid":1475834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"破解不反對通知書制度，一人一遊行申請","createTime":"2019-08-15T15:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:32:40.000Z","uid":272074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"905f04d859eddf18a09f77435d7230b0bd9bda66","tid":1475834,"uid":272074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"其實要申請遊行唔係咁難<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/licences/poess.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Flicences%2Fpoess.html&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=b42fac30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/licences/poess.html</a><br />\n去呢個網download 張form ，只需要填你嘅個人資料，遊行路線、目的嗰啲可以求奇寫，再交去指定狗屋<br />\n<br />\n只要狗反對你遊行而你決定上訴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗就需要舉行上訴委員會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地可以發動其中一個weekend 一人一申請，如果狗反對，就要幾日內舉行無數個上訴委員會，用行政程序玩死佢<br />\n<br />\n相反如果佢批准嘅，我地就去行。只要做到一次，啲狗以後就唔敢隨便反對"},{"pid":"8fdb78acaa83f879f386c75c7056d6fa38acd266","tid":1475834,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b3ec477d442c972f48f6c4542e8eb56b30306e","tid":1475834,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4b5654eb89c0fac19f0ed612f7bd3d08cfdc148","tid":1475834,"uid":272074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:25:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9562b571e15d2a4a8850ee947a531144aea6882","tid":1475834,"uid":261585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"幫推10<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor